::Zardus/Havoc/Demolition::

Zardus nods. "We are moving into another base right now, so there 
will soon be lots to do. But the Alliance switches a;;ies often, we 
could be allied with the Maximals soon. You'll need to think of a way 
to kill Arcangel without giving away your alliegence."

He looks the bot over, seeing his resemblence to Arcangel. Zardus 
turns his head as Havoc flies up behind him.

"This femm needs CR attention," Havoc says, "How soon will we reach 
the new base?"

"Fairly soon," Zardus says, "I'm going to fly ahead, you may come 
with me. But first..."

He glances at his wrist comp, noting that Feline's bodyparts were 
still in the CR (Hot Rod put them in there).

"Can you go to the CR chambers, take Feline's body out, and bring her 
to the Iron Fist? I'll take Squizzy."

Havoc nods, handing over Squizzy and flying back toward the 
scientific section of the base.

"Demolition," Zardus says into his comm, "Please go to the cargo 
holds and find a box labeled 'Delta'. He's a warrior from the past, 
and I'm planning to revive him. Bring him to the Iron FIst when you 
find him."

"Allright," Demolition's voice replies, the jet flying toward the 
cargo section.

"Now," Zardus says, turning back to Dark Angel, "Do you want to 
accompany me to the new base?"
